TAGS="daemon internet connections"
COMMENTS=" Add to /opt/bootlocal.sh :
                        /usr/local/etc/init.d/dbus start
                        connmand
                or connmand -r as in my case.
		For persistency add var/lib/connman/ to 
		/opt/.filetool.lst
                ---
                optional dep: wpa_supplicant-dbus.tcz"
